  },
  "kind" : "article",
  "metadata" : {
    "role" : "article",
    "roleHeading" : "Article",
    "title" : "External dependencies"
  },
  "primaryContentSections" : [
    {
      "content" : [
        {
          "anchor" : "overview",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Overview",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Embedded Swift minimizes external dependencies (i.e. functions that need to be available at link-time), but they still exist. There are generally two categories of dependencies: (1) functions that the Swift standard library or Embedded Swift runtime need to call, and (2) functions\/symbols that are implicitly added by LLVM and the compiler pipeline.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "For (1), external dependencies are only used based on actual usage of the program under compilation:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "instantiating a class, or using UnsafeMutablePointer.allocate()",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency: ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "int posix_memalign(void **, size_t, size_t);",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency: ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "void free(void *);",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "using print()",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency: ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "int putchar(int);",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "using Hashable, Set, Dictionary, or random-number generating APIs",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency: ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "void arc4random_buf(void *, size_t);",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "For (2), external dependencies are also triggered by specific code needing them, but they are somewhat lower-level patterns where it might not be obvious that such patterns should cause external dependencies:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "basic memory copying and zeroing functions",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "usage added for a variety of reasons (e.g. using structs on the stack)",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency: ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "void *memset(void *, int, size_t);",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency: ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "void *memcpy(void *, const void *, size_t);",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "stack protectors",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " (aka stack cookies or stack canaries)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency: ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "void *__stack_chk_guard;",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency: ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "void __stack_chk_fail(void);",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "stack protectors can be disabled with ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "-disable-stack-protector",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : " swiftc flag",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "atomics intrinsics",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "on CPU architectures that don’t have direct load-acquire\/store-release support in the ISA, LLVM calls helper functions for atomic operations",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "needed by refcounting in the Embedded Swift runtime (so any class usage will trigger this dependency)",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "also needed when using atomics from the Synchronization module",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "multiplication\/division\/modulo intrinsics",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "on CPU architectures that don’t have direct support for the math operations in the ISA",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency (on Mach-O): ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "__divti3",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency (on Mach-O): ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "__modti3",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "dependency (with EABI): ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "__aeabi_ldivmod",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "dynamic exclusivity checking",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " (enabled with ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code" : "-enforce-exclusivity=checked",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : ")",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "for single-threaded environments, link ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "swiftExclusivitySingleThreaded",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : " library",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "for multi-threaded environments that support C++11 thread-local storage, link ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "code" : "swiftExclusivityC11ThreadLocal",
                              "type" : "codeVoice"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "for environments where neither of the above will suffice",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        },
                        {
                          "items" : [
                            {
                              "content" : [
                                {
                                  "inlineContent" : [
                                    {
                                      "text" : "dependency: ",
                                      "type" : "text"
                                    },
                                    {
                                      "code" : "void * _swift_getExclusivityTLS()",
                                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                                    }
                                  ],
                                  "type" : "paragraph"
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "content" : [
                                {
                                  "inlineContent" : [
                                    {
                                      "text" : "dependency: void ",
                                      "type" : "text"
                                    },
                                    {
                                      "code" : "_swift_setExclusivityTLS(void *newValue)",
                                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                                    }
                                  ],
                                  "type" : "paragraph"
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "unorderedList"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The user and\/or the platform (via basic libraries like libc or compiler builtins) is expected to provide these APIs.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        }
      ],
